title: The Foundry Modo 11.2v1 (win/64bit)
description: 7 November 2017 MODO is the unique, artist-friendly 3D software that combines modeling, painting, animation and rendering in a fused workflow for designers and artists working in the areas of industrial design, architectural visualization, package design, game development, film and broadcast, education and scientific studies.
